sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import {Button, Modal, ModalBody, ModalCloseButton, ModalContent, ModalFooter, ModalHeader, ModalOverlay, useDisclosure,} from "@chakra-ui/react"; const GroupChatModal = ({children}) => { const { isOpen, onOpen, onClose } = useDisclosure(); const [groupChatName, setGroupChatName] = useState(); return ( <> {children} Modal Title ) } export default GroupChatModal
